rComments: She was very reasonable in dealing with students, and honestly wants everyone to do well in her class.  Sometimes the content is a bit boring and there is a lot of busy work, but it's kind of a nice break from hard papers and tests.

This whole class was about learning what you want to do for a career. Tiffany was beyond helpful in everything.  She was really nice and approachable and I could tell her about my feelings about what I wanted to do. Veryaccepting and very fun class.
